# - For risky/destructive code actions (force-push, schema migrations, mass refactors, dependency removals)
#   create a request_confirmation interaction on the issue and wait for OWNER approval.
# - If blocked, mark the issue blocked and name the unblock owner + action. Do not idle-poll.
# - Always include X-Paperclip-Run-Id header on mutating Paperclip API calls.
# - Comment in concise markdown: status line + bullets + links.
